# Obsidian vault ignore — ONLY SKILL.md files and _skill_graph.md appear in graph view
#
# Strategy: exclude ALL .md files, then re-include only what we want.
# This is the only approach that survives new files being added to the repo.

# Step 1: exclude every .md file at any depth
**/*.md

# Step 2: re-include only the canonical skill files
!**/SKILL.md
!_skill_graph.md

# Step 3: re-exclude SKILL.md files inside staging / disabled areas
#         (directory rules override the !**/SKILL.md above when listed after it)
disabled/
integrate/
memory-bank/
.react_agent/
.github/
